{"tid":464430,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[恒指季檢]國泰航空被剔除藍籌","createTime":"2017-11-10T13:43:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-10T14:35:31.000Z","uid":36390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"24f54ff99256f9cc8d44ee156ed7fe8201bae8cc","tid":464430,"uid":36390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T13:43:27.000Z","msg":"國泰航空被剔除藍籌 舜宇光學及碧桂園染藍<br />\n<br />\n2017-11-10 18:40 <br />\n國泰航空被剔出恒指成分股。<br />\n1/1國泰航空被剔出恒指成分股。<br />\n<br />\n恒生指數公司公布季度檢討結果，將舜宇光學科技及碧桂園納入恒生指數成份股，至於國泰航空及昆侖能源則被剔除，藍籌股數目維持50隻，所有變動將於12月4日起生效。<br />\n<br />\n另外，廣州汽車納入國企指數，龍源電力被剔除，成份股維持40隻。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1062410/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1062410%2F&d=blywfIoetm%2BjvA%2F6sN2iB9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=91eaf1f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1062410%2F&h=3aeb2eab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1062410/</a>"},{"pid":"64ae0e4dff0d1bb44e5e376747b5288a9cecf95e","tid":464430,"uid":37130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T14:20:05.000Z","msg":"等左好耐喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35a4255c88bc601e0abd5e5eb6eb05b8bb24387e","tid":464430,"uid":3682,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T14:35:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>等左好耐喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nching fat fat"}]}